WEBVTT

00:00.666 --> 00:02.083
(MUSIC PLAYING)

00:05.166 --> 00:07.374
ROCKET: Get back here,
you pointy-haired freak!

00:07.374 --> 00:09.541
Filthy bounty hunters,
leave me alone!

00:09.541 --> 00:11.249
Don't let him
get away, Groot!

00:11.249 --> 00:12.749
That shapeshifter's worth
half a million credits.

00:12.749 --> 00:14.208
I am Groot!

00:15.582 --> 00:16.374
(GRUNTING)

00:20.707 --> 00:21.749
(YELLS)

00:22.957 --> 00:24.083
Huh!
(BEEPS)

00:26.374 --> 00:27.499
(MUMBLES)

00:27.499 --> 00:29.915
(GROANING) Huh?

00:29.915 --> 00:31.666
What are you waiting for?
Get him!

00:31.666 --> 00:33.666
Don't fall for that.
He's the bounty.
Come on.

00:33.666 --> 00:35.166
(MUMBLING)

00:38.707 --> 00:39.457
(BOTH YELP)

00:41.832 --> 00:43.582
He's the imposter!
This is ridiculous!

00:43.582 --> 00:45.000
Groot! Come on!
It's me!

00:45.000 --> 00:46.915
I am Groot.

00:46.915 --> 00:49.333
I'm the real Rocket.
Look, I know
I don't tell you enough,

00:49.333 --> 00:50.915
but we've been through a lot.

00:50.915 --> 00:54.541
And I would never wanna
face the galaxy without you
by my side.

00:54.541 --> 00:56.416
Aw. Mmm?

00:57.624 --> 00:59.832
(CLEARS THROAT)

00:59.832 --> 01:01.291
You, wood for brains,
waste of space!

01:01.291 --> 01:02.582
I'm gonna bust
your branches

01:02.582 --> 01:04.083
if you don't get me
outta here right now!

01:06.041 --> 01:07.457
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

01:07.457 --> 01:09.666
I am Groot!

01:09.666 --> 01:11.666
Yeah, yeah, me too.

01:11.666 --> 01:14.666
So, what are we
gonna do with our
shapeshifting friend?

01:17.624 --> 01:19.041
Hey, stop playing with that!

01:19.041 --> 01:20.124
I am Groot.

01:20.790 --> 01:22.041
(SQUEAKING)

01:22.041 --> 01:23.249
I don't like this!

01:23.249 --> 01:24.624
(LAUGHS)
(BEEPING)

01:24.624 --> 01:26.790
Come on, Groot, try it.
It's a blast.
(COW MOOING)

01:26.790 --> 01:28.291
I am Groot.
